title: 11/26/21 DPS Hour 1
itunes:title: 11/26/21 DPS Hour 1
description:
Rob Parker and Jason McIntyre, in for Dan, react to the Cowboys losing to the Raiders on Thanksgiving, and Rob explains why he believes the Cowboys are frauds. The guys break down why they both believe the Lions will finish the season without at win. Former NFL Scout and Buccaneers Beat Writer Leo Haggerty joins the guys to give his thoughts on the NFC playoff race and break down the Bucs matchup with the Colts this weekend. Plus, the guys discuss the state of the Lakers as LeBron James continues to miss action.
